quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nuun, M wẽen ne kaal-moogo, la bũmb ning b sẽn gʋlsdã."
  68,2,"Fo pa yɩ ne f Soabã neema wã n yaa gãeeng ye."
  68,3,"La fo tara keoor sẽn pa wãagde."
  68,4,"La foo, fo bee zʋgd sẽn zɩs zugu."
  68,5,"Lɑ fo na yã, la bãmb me na yã."
  68,6,"Yãmb sʋkã b sẽn zarb-a soab t'ɑ yɑɑ gãeengɑ."
  68,7,"Bãng tɩ fo Soabã, Yẽ n yɩɩd minim ne ned ning sẽn menem-a n bas A sorã, Yẽ n leb n yɩɩd minim ne kãndgdbã."
  68,8,"Bɩ f ra tũ yagsdbã ye."
  68,9,"B maana nonglem tɩ fo bars tɩ b me barse."
  68,10,"La f ra tũ wẽen toog soab fãa sẽn yaa nin-yaalg ye."
  68,11,"N yaa zangda, n yaa kẽn-toog soab ne tẽnkãnem."
  68,12,"N yaa sõma gɩdg-toog soaba, n yaa maan-n-zʋʋgd n yaa tʋʋm-beed soaba."
  68,13,"N yaa tõata, rẽ poorẽ n yaa yel-beed soaba."
  68,14,"Tɩ bɑlɑ ɑ yɩɩme n ya ligd la koamb soab yĩnga."
  68,15,"B sã n karemd a zug Tõnd aayayã a yetame ɑd yɑɑ: ""pĩnd rãmb yẽsgo""."
  68,16,"D na n ning-a-la bãnd a yão-raongã zugu."
  68,17,"Tõnd zarba bãmb wala D sẽn zarb pʋʋgã rãmbã, wakat ning b sẽn wa n wẽen tɩ b na kẽeb-a be-vẽegre."
  68,18,"La b pa yeel tɩ ""Wẽnd sã n sak"" ye."
  68,19,"Tɩ gilgd gilg a zug sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn gõe."
  68,20,"T'a yik yibeoogã n legb wala yʋʋn-lik."
  68,21,"Tɩ b vẽeg beoog n bool taaba."
  68,22,"""Tɩ y sãd-y yã n tʋg yãmb pʋʋgẽ wã tɩ y sã n yaa kẽebdba""."
  68,23,"Tɩ b yi tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn walamd taaba:"
  68,24,"""Ned kõn kẽ rũndã yãmb nengẽ sẽn ya ninbãan-ned ye""."
  68,25,"Tɩ b sãd pĩndã, n gãd tɩ bãmb yaa tõogdba."
  68,26,"La wakat ning b sẽn wa n yã-a wã b yeelame: ""tõnd tudga zĩiga."
  68,27,"Pa woto ye! Tõnd yaa b sẽn mong-b rãmba."
  68,28,"Tɩ sẽn yɩɩd-a ne bʋʋmã yeele: ""m da pa yeel yãmba! Yãmb sã n da yɩlg Wẽnde! (pɑ yɩtẽ woto ye)"
  68,29,"Tɩ b yeele:""yɩlgr be ne tõnd Soabã, tõnd da yɩɩme n yaa wẽgdba""."
  68,30,"Tɩ b togl taab n sãbsd taaba."
  68,31,"N yeele: ""yaa tõnd wɩɩbdo! Tõnd da yɩɩme n yaa kεdgdba""."
  68,32,"Sãnd-sãnd tõnd Soabã na tedg ne tõnd sõma sẽn yɩɩd-a, ad tõnd maanda yamleoog n tʋg d Soaba nengẽ."
  68,33,"Namsgã me yaa woto bala, la ad Laahr naongã n yɩɩde, tɩ bãmb sã n da miime."
  68,34,"Ad wẽn-zoetbã tarame b Soabã nengẽ, neema Arzãn-rãmba."
  68,35,"Rẽ yĩnga tõnd na maan sẽn sak n tũ-bã wala nin-wẽmsã ?"
  68,36,"Yaa bõe n tar yãmb tɩ y bʋʋd woto?"
  68,37,"Bɩ yãmb tara gafo? T'a pʋgẽ la yãmb karemda?"
  68,38,"Tɩ be ne yãmb ɑ pʋgẽ, yãmb sẽn tũusdi."
  68,39,"Bɩ yãmb tara pʋlems Tõnd zug sẽn ka tεkɑ, n tɩ tãag Rũni yikr raare? Tɩ be rẽ pʋgẽ n yetẽ Ad be ne yãmba, bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tũus n dɑt-ɑ."
  68,40,"Sok-ba: yaa bãmb nin-bʋg n na n reeg a zugẽ ne rẽ?"
  68,41,"Bɩ bãmb tara lagem-n-taase; bɩ b wa ne b lagem-n-taasã tɩ b sã n yaa sɩd rãmba."
  68,42,"Raar ning B sẽn na n pidg kargɑ, la b boond bãmb n tʋgd Suguudu tɩ bãmb pa tõe ye."
  68,43,"Tɩ b nin yaa sẽn nodge, tɩ yaoolg bui-ba. La sɩd la hakɩɩka, b ra yɩɩme n boond-b n tʋgd Suguudã tɩ b ra yaa laafɩ rãmba."
  68,44,"Bɩ f bas Maam ne ned ning sẽn yagsd-a gom-kãensã, D na n paam-b lame zĩig ning b sẽn pa mi."
  68,45,"La M yaoond-b lame, ad Mam rabrã kegmame."
  68,46,"Bɩ fo sokd-b-la keoore, tɩ bãmb be samd pʋgẽ tɩ zɩsg b zugu."
  68,47,"Bɩ bãmb tara sẽn solge, tɩ bãmb gʋlsdẽ."
  68,48,"Bɩ f maan sugr ne f Soabã Bʋʋdã, la f ra wa yɩ wala zĩunfã soab ye; wakat ning a sẽn wa n bool ɑ Soɑbã tɩ yẽnda yaa sũ-toog soaba."
  68,49,"La sã n da pa neema sẽn paam-a, neema sẽn yi a Soabã nengẽ, b rag n na lobg-a weo-raoogẽ t'a yaa b sẽn sãgbs-a soaba."
  68,50,"T'a Soabã tũus-a n ning-a nin-sõmsẽ wã."
  68,51,"La sẽn kɩfl-bã ra pẽnegame n na n guug foo ne b ninã, wakat ning b sẽn wa n wʋm Alkʋrãanã, la b yetẽ: ""ad a sɩd yaa gãeenga""."
  68,52,"Lɑ Alkʋrãanã pa yɩ, rẽnda tẽegr ne bõn-nãandsã."
